       <div class="titSub">
        <h1 id="titleCn">为什么我努力爱麦当娜</h1>
        <a href="javascript:;" class="btn1 editBtn">修改标题</a>
       </div> 
       <p class="author">作者：<a href="/search/Matthew%20Harris/" target="_blank"> Matthew Harris</a></p> 
       <p class="titBar"> <span class="time">时间：2012-09-19</span> <span class="read">阅读：3065</span> <span class="source">来源：<a href="http://www.buzzfeed.com/matthewharris/why-i-struggle-to-love-madonna" target="_blank" rel="“nofollow”">buzzfeed</a></span> </p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="span2"> 
       <div class="recom"> 
        <div class="recomBox " data-article_id="3322ca76bfaca980228cfc9c58c2b3d4"> 
         <p class="num">6</p> 
         <p class="txt">推荐</p> 
        </div> 
